      <abstract>
        <p>SmarterKids.com, an online educational store and resource for parents, assigns ad account to Orsatti &amp; Partners, Boston (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>SmarterKids.com, Needham, Mass., an online educational store and resource for parents, to Orsatti &amp; Partners, Boston, to handle its account, which had been at Mullen, Wenham, Mass., part of the Lowe Group unit of the Interpublic Group of Cos. Billings were estimated at $5 million to $7 million.</p>
      </block>
